# --- Confidential data — NEVER commit ---
# Source PDFs (statement scans), parsed Markdown (statement headers
# contain name/address/sort code/account), the DuckDB ledger, the wiki
# auto-generated from real transactions, the compiled Kuzu graph, and
# the OpenAI audit log all derive from real personal finance data.
# Anchored to the repo root so a `web/app/graph/` route or other nested
# directory with these names is NOT excluded.
/sources/
/parsed/
/wiki/
/data/
/graph/
/out/
/eval/out/
.env
.env.local
*.duckdb
*.duckdb.wal
*.duckdb-tmp

# Local Claude Code session state
.claude/

# pyvis auto-extracts vis.js/tom-select bundles next to graph.html
# (anchored to root so web/lib/ etc. aren't excluded)
/lib/

